and download “jdk 6 update 4”[/quote]

That’s False.

They are currently on Update 5

Plus if your using “The Perfect Compiler” , you need to change the classpath inside the compiler. Which would be forund by: Right Click - > Edit

Change it to the JDK you have downloaded.
